<p>Hello <%= @resource.first_name %>,</p>
<p>
This message was sent to you because someone requested that a password reset be sent to the verified email address associated with your account. If you requested this, you can continue to log in.
</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="mcnButtonContentContainer" style="border-collapse: separate !important;border-radius: 3px;background-color: #15C0F1; margin: auto">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td align="center" valign="middle" class="mcnButtonContent" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; padding: 15px;">
        <%= link_to "Reset Password", edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), {style:"font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 100%;text-align: center;text-decoration: none;color: #FFFFFF;"} %>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>If you did not request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email.&nbsp;Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.<br>

<p>Thank you, <br/>
The MortgageClub Team</p>